msgid "OBJECTIVE: Locate and recover neural synapse technology"
msgstr "SCOPVS: Technologiam neuronicae synapseos locare ac recolligere"

msgid "Establish a base, then search for a Pre-Collapse structure."
msgstr "Basin instituere, dein structuram pro ruinā quaerere."

msgid "This structure contains technology vital for the success of the Project."
msgstr "Haec structura technologiam continet ad Consilium prosepere procedendum necassariam."

msgid "ALPHA BASE MISSION: Scavenger Raiders"
msgstr "MISSIO BASEOS ALPHA: Praedatores Cloacarii"

msgid "Scavenger raiders are approaching our base."
msgstr "Praedatores cloacarii ad basin nostram accedunt."

msgid "Defend the base then destroy the Scavenger camps."
msgstr "Basin defendere, et deinde Cloacariorum castra delere."

msgid "ALPHA BASE MISSION: Power Surge Detected"
msgstr "MISSIO BASEOS ALPHA: Potentiae Fluctus Deprehensus"

msgid "A power surge has been detected to the south of our position."
msgstr "Incrementum electricum ad meridiem a positione nostra detecta est."

msgid "Investigate and secure the area."
msgstr "Aream scrutari ac tutam facere."

msgid "ALPHA BASE MISSION: The New Paradigm"
msgstr "MISSIO BASEOS ALPHA: Paradigma Novum"

msgid "The New Paradigm control superior weapons technology."
msgstr "Novum Paradigma technologiam armorum superiorem regit."

msgid "They may have the synaptic link technology, it's vital we retrieve it."
msgstr "Fortasse technologiam nexus synaptici habent, magni momenti est ut eam recuperemus."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Locate and Recover Artifacts"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSPORTUS: Artefacta Locare et Recuperare"

msgid "Load an attack force into the transport."
msgstr "Copias impetum faciendi in vehiculum onerarium impone."

msgid "On landing, explore the ruins and recover any artifacts."
msgstr "Cum appuleris, ruinas explora et quaevis artefacta recupera."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Investigate Research Center"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSPORTUS: Centrum Investigationis Investigare"

msgid "Investigate the area and recover any artifacts present."
msgstr "Regionem investiga et quaecumque artefacta praesentia recupera."

msgid "Reinforcements are available."
msgstr "Subsisium ad manum est."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Encoded Signals Detected"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSPORTUS: Signa Codificata Detecta"

msgid "Take a scout force to investigate these signals."
msgstr "Duc manum exploratorum ad haec signa investiganda."

msgid "Use your trucks to build defenses at your LZ."
msgstr "Utere vehiculis tuis ad munimenta in LZ tua construenda."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Enemy Transmissions Detected"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSPORTUS: Transmissiones Hostium Detectae"

msgid "Scout the designated area for enemy research facilities."
msgstr "Regionem designatam ad loca investigationis hostium explora."

msgid "Proceed to LZ#2. Do not engage the enemy at this time."
msgstr "Ad LZ#2 procede. Noli hostem hoc tempore aggredi."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Synaptic Link Location"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSPORTATIONIS: Situs Nexus Synaptici"

msgid "The New Paradigm are analyzing synaptic link technology at this location."
msgstr "Novum Paradigma technologiam nexus synaptici in hoc loco examinat."

msgid "Assemble an attack team and recover the synaptic link technology."
msgstr "Coetum impetus faciendi congrega et technologiam nexus synaptici recupera."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: New Objectives"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSPORTUS: Nova Proposita"

msgid "New Paradigm are searching for artifacts in this vicinity."
msgstr "Novum Paradigma artefacta in hac vicinitate quaerit."

msgid "Intercept them. Do not let any enemies exit this area."
msgstr "Intercipe eos. Ne sinas ullos hostes ex hac regione exire."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Enemy Base Under Construction"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSPORTUS: Basis Hostilis Sub Constructione"

msgid "Enemy forces are establishing a forward base at this location."
msgstr "Copiae hostium castra anteriora hoc loco constituunt."

msgid "Eradicate the base and secure the area."
msgstr "Basis deleatur et regionem securetur."

msgid "ALPHA BASE MISSION: Establish a Forward Base"
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS ALPHA: Constituere Basin Progredientem"

msgid "Establish a forward base on the plateau and fend off the New Paradigm."
msgstr "Castra anteriora in planitie constitue et Novum Paradigma propulsa."

msgid "Build defensive structures until the green objective blip disappears."
msgstr "Structuras defensivas construe donec signum viride obiectivum evanescat."

msgid "ALPHA BASE MISSION: Counter Attack"
msgstr "MISSIO BASEOS ALPHA: Impetus Adversarius"

msgid "Enemy forces are approaching from the east and north."
msgstr "Copiae hostium ab oriente et septentrione appropinquant."

msgid "Hold the bases and repulse any attacks."
msgstr "Tene bases et omnes impetus repelle."

msgid "ALPHA BASE MISSION: Incoming Transmission"
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS ALPHA: Transmissio Adveniens"

msgid "We are detecting enemy forces at these locations."
msgstr "Copias hostium his in locis deprehendimus."

msgid "This is our chance to defeat the New Paradigm and destroy their base."
msgstr "Haec est occasio nostra ut Novum Paradigma vincamus et basim eorum deleamus."

msgid "Congratulations Commander."
msgstr "Gratulationes, Centurio."

msgid "We now have a further task for you."
msgstr "Nunc aliud munus tibi habemus."

msgid "ALPHA BASE MISSION: Locate and Recover Artifacts"
msgstr "MISSIO BASEOS ALPHA: Locare atque recolligere artificiata"

msgid "The first two zones are now secure."
msgstr "Primae duae zonae nunc tutae sunt."

msgid "PROJECT TEAM UPDATES"
msgstr "NOVA TURMARUM INCEPTI"

msgid "TEAM BETA UPDATE"
msgstr "GREGIS BETA RENOVATIO"

msgid "We have recovered some artifacts."
msgstr "Aliqua artificia recuperavimus."

msgid "There is a better equipped force operating in this area."
msgstr "Copiae melius instructae in hac regione versantur."

msgid "TEAM GAMMA UPDATE"
msgstr "GREGIS GAMMA RENOVATIO"

msgid "Nothing to report."
msgstr "Nihil renuntiandum."

msgid "We've discovered no artifacts and encountered no hostiles."
msgstr "Nulla artificia invenimus et nullos hostes offendimus."

msgid "ALPHA BASE INTELLIGENCE REPORT: Enemy Attack"
msgstr "RELATIO EXPLORATORIA BASIS ALPHA: Impetus Hostium"

msgid "We are detecting an enemy attack force at this location."
msgstr "Copias oppugnatorias hostium hoc in loco deprehendimus."

msgid "PRIMARY OBJECTIVE"
msgstr "SCOPVS PRIMVS"

msgid "This structure is your primary objective."
msgstr "Haec structura est propositum tuum primarium."

msgid "Search for and recover any artifacts here."
msgstr "Hic artificia quaelibet quaere et recupera."

msgid "ENEMY LZ"
msgstr "ZONA APPULSUS HOSTIUM"

msgid "Destroy this LZ to prevent enemy landings."
msgstr "Hanc zonam appulsus dele, ne hostes descendant."

msgid "ALPHA BASE INTELLIGENCE REPORT: NEXUS"
msgstr "RELATIO EXPLORATORIA BASIS ALPHA: NEXUS"

msgid "New objective."
msgstr "Scopus novus."

msgid "We have detected and isolated an intruder program."
msgstr "Programma irruptoris deprehendimus et seiunximus."

msgid "Supplemental"
msgstr "Supplementum"

msgid "The synaptic link technology was at this location but was removed."
msgstr "Technologia nexus synaptici hoc in loco erat sed remota est."

msgid "Establish a forward base then continue the search for the synaptic link."
msgstr "Basim anteriorem constitue, deinde nexum synapticum quaerere perge."

msgid "INCOMING TRANSMISSION"
msgstr "TRANSMISSIO ADVENIENS"

msgid "Decoding in progress....."
msgstr "Enodatio in fieri....."

msgid "Commander."
msgstr "Centurio."

msgid "We have decoded the incoming message to the New Paradigm..."
msgstr "Nuntium ad Novum Paradigma missum deciphravimus..."

msgid "Destroy Enemy Base"
msgstr "Dele Basim Hostium"

msgid "Assemble an attack force and board the transport."
msgstr "Copias oppugnatorias congrega et transvectorium conscende."

msgid "Destroy the base and recover any artifacts present."
msgstr "Basim dele et artificia quaelibet praesentia recupera."

msgid "The synaptic link technology has been recovered!"
msgstr "Technologia nexus synaptici recuperata est!"

msgid "Initial research confirms it will be of great benefit to the Project."
msgstr "Investigatio prima confirmat id Incepto magno beneficio fore."

msgid "Base Beta is under heavy attack, they may need assistance."
msgstr "Basis Beta gravi impetu petitur; fortasse auxilio indigebunt."

msgid "We will send further updates as they arrive."
msgstr "Plura nova mittemus cum advenerint."

msgid "This transmission was intercepted a few minutes ago."
msgstr "Haec transmissio ante paucas minutas intercepta est."

msgid "It originates from the east."
msgstr "Ex oriente oritur."

msgid "POWER MODULE ARTIFACT"
msgstr "ARTIFICIUM MODULI POTENTIAE"

msgid "Research the power module artifact."
msgstr "Artificium moduli potentiae investiga."

msgid "Then use a truck to upgrade your power generator with the module."
msgstr "Deinde autocarro utere ut generatorem potentiae tuum hoc modulo augeas."

msgid "SCAVENGER BASE DETECTED"
msgstr "BASIS PRAEDONUM DEPREHENSA"

msgid "Defeat the scavengers and retrieve any artifacts."
msgstr "Praedones vince et artificia quaelibet recupera."

msgid "Congratulations on defeating the New Paradigm, this sector is now secure."
msgstr "Gratulamur tibi quod Novum Paradigma vicisti; hic sector nunc tutus est."

msgid "The Nexus Intruder Program was in the New Paradigm system."
msgstr "Programma Irruptoris Nexus in systemate Novi Paradigmatis erat."

msgid "We recorded two conversations with it, extracts follow..."
msgstr "Duo colloquia cum eo registravimus; excerpta sequuntur..."

msgid "We'll keep you informed of further developments"
msgstr "Te de ulterioribus rebus certiorem faciemus"

msgid "Commander you are to assist Team Beta"
msgstr "Praefecte, Turmae Beta auxilium feres"

msgid "BETA BASE MISSION: Eastern Sector"
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS BETA: Sector Orientalis"

msgid "Upon arrival you are to assume command of the base."
msgstr "Cum adveneris, imperium basis suscipies."

msgid "You must defend it and hold it."
msgstr "Eam defendere et tenere debes."

msgid "BETA BASE MISSION: Defend and Fortify"
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS BETA: Defende et Muni"

msgid "Be sure to fortify the perimeter and establish anti-aircraft defenses."
msgstr "Cura ut perimetrum munias et defensiones contra aeronaves constituas."

msgid "New technologies are available."
msgstr "Novae technologiae praesto sunt."

msgid "We are currently detecting coded bitstream signals."
msgstr "Nunc signa cifrata fluxus datorum deprehendimus."

msgid "Decoding..."
msgstr "Enodatur..."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Transport Down"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Transvectorium Deiectum"

msgid "Our transport carrying units from team Alpha Base has been shot down."
msgstr "Transvectorium nostrum, quod copias e Basi Alpha vehebat, deiectum est."

msgid "It is under attack from The Collective at this location."
msgstr "A Communitate hoc in loco oppugnatur."

msgid "Assemble a rescue team to recover the transport and its cargo."
msgstr "Manum servatricem congrega ut transvectorium et onus eius recuperes."

msgid "IN-FLIGHT BRIEFING"
msgstr "PRAEFATIO IN VOLATU"

msgid "Team Beta are searching for Vertical Takeoff and Landing (VTOL) technology."
msgstr "Turma Beta technologiam Decollationis et Appulsus Verticalis (DEAV) quaerit."

msgid "It's believed to be at a pre-Collapse airbase in this area."
msgstr "Creditur in basi aeria ante Ruinam in hac regione esse."

msgid "Team Beta under heavy attack"
msgstr "Turma Beta gravi impetu petitur"

msgid "BETA BASE MISSION: Hold at all costs"
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS BETA: Tene Quolibet Pretio"

msgid "We are detecting coded bitstream signals from the Collective."
msgstr "Signa cifrata fluxus datorum a Communitate deprehendimus."

msgid "BETA BASE MISSION: Hold At All Costs"
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS BETA: Tene Quolibet Pretio"

msgid "We are detecting ground and aerial forces from the north."
msgstr "Copias terrestres et aerias a septentrione deprehendimus."

msgid "Hold your position and repulse these attacks, then eradicate the enemy's northern base."
msgstr "Locum tene et hos impetus repelle, deinde basim septentrionalem hostis dele."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Intercept convoy."
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Intercipe commeatum."

msgid "Data from the Collective's base indicates the presence of the NEXUS intruder program."
msgstr "Data e basi Communitatis praesentiam programmatis irruptoris NEXUS indicant."

msgid "Before NEXUS switched itself off-line we accessed the following."
msgstr "Antequam NEXUS se ipsum extra rete posuit, haec accessimus."

msgid "An enemy commander is collecting a shipment from NEXUS at this location."
msgstr "Praefectus hostium onus a NEXUS hoc in loco colligit."

msgid "Once at the LZ, eradicate the enemy commander and recover the shipment."
msgstr "Cum ad zonam appulsus perveneris, praefectum hostium dele et onus recupera."

msgid "Then return to the LZ."
msgstr "Deinde ad zonam appulsus redi."

msgid "Disturbing news regarding NASDA."
msgstr "Nova turbantia de NASDA."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Search for and Destroy Convoy"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Quaere et Dele Commeatum"

msgid "The shipment you recovered was a decoy."
msgstr "Onus quod recuperavisti fallax erat."

msgid "We have detected another convoy proceeding along the river."
msgstr "Alium commeatum secundum flumen procedentem deprehendimus."

msgid "You are to intercept the convoy and recover its cargo."
msgstr "Commeatum intercipere et onus eius recuperare debes."

msgid "Enemy VTOLs are likely to be flying close escort."
msgstr "DEAV hostium verisimiliter prope volabunt ut custodiam praestent."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Rescue civilians from Containment Camp"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Serva Cives e Castris Detentionis"

msgid "The Collective are processing and exterminating civilians at this base."
msgstr "Communitas cives in hac basi tractat et exterminat."

msgid "You are to rescue the civilians."
msgstr "Cives servare debes."

msgid "Then destroy the camp."
msgstr "Deinde castra dele."

msgid "BETA BASE MISSION: Destroy Enemy Air Base and Recover VTOLs."
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS BETA: Dele Basim Aeriam Hostium et Recupera DEAV."

msgid "Analysis of flight paths indicate that The Collective's VTOLs originate from here."
msgstr "Analysis viarum volatus indicat DEAV Communitatis hinc oriri."

msgid "BETA BASE MISSION: Destroy Enemy Air Base and Recover VTOLs"
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS BETA: Dele Basim Aeriam Hostium et Recupera DEAV"

msgid "The location of the enemy airbase is here; this is your primary objective."
msgstr "Locus basis aeriae hostium hic est; hoc est propositum tuum primarium."

msgid "Eradicate all Collective forces and recover all artifacts."
msgstr "Omnes copias Communitatis dele et omnia artificia recupera."

msgid "SECONDARY MISSION: Destroy or Drive Off Enemy Transport"
msgstr "MISSIO SECUNDARIA: Dele vel Pelle Transvectorium Hostium"

msgid "The Collective are rounding up all civilians in this area."
msgstr "Communitas omnes cives in hac regione cogit."

msgid "They are then flying them to an unknown location."
msgstr "Deinde eos ad locum ignotum avehunt."

msgid "Destroy or drive off The Collective's transport."
msgstr "Transvectorium Communitatis dele vel pelle."

msgid "Rescue as many civilians as possible."
msgstr "Quam plurimos cives serva."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Destroy Reactor"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Dele Reactorem"

msgid "The Collective are searching for knowledge of nuclear reactors."
msgstr "Communitas scientiam reactorum nuclearium quaerit."

msgid "They must be stopped."
msgstr "Prohibendi sunt."

msgid "Proceed from the LZ to the reactor and destroy it."
msgstr "A zona appulsus ad reactorem procede et eum dele."

msgid "Do not allow the Collective to bring the reactor on-line."
msgstr "Noli sinere Communitatem reactorem activare."

msgid "BETA BASE MISSION: Capture NASDA Central"
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS BETA: Occupa NASDA Centrale"

msgid "Capture NASDA central before NEXUS and the Collective can use it."
msgstr "Occupa NASDA centrale antequam NEXUS et Communitas eo uti possint."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Satellite Uplink Site"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Statio Conexionis Satellitis"

msgid "NEXUS is searching for still functioning memory banks."
msgstr "NEXUS cellas memoriae adhuc operantes quaerit."

msgid "Part of its consciousness has moved to a remote NASDA control-site."
msgstr "Pars conscientiae eius ad remotam stationem moderatricem NASDA migravit."

msgid "We are detecting transmissions from this site that are reaching high orbit."
msgstr "Transmissiones ab hoc loco quae altam orbitam attingunt deprehendimus."

msgid "NEXUS has now reconnected itself with the NASDA satellites."
msgstr "NEXUS se ipsum cum satellitibus NASDA nunc reconexuit."

msgid "Use the transport to carry a strike force to this site."
msgstr "Transvectorio utere ut manum oppugnatoriam ad hunc locum vehas."

msgid "Destroy the site and return to your base."
msgstr "Locum dele et ad basim tuam redi."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Destroy Enemy SAM Sites"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Dele Stationes Missilium Hostium"

msgid "If you are to escape, eradicate the surface-to-air missile sites around your base."
msgstr "Si effugere vis, stationes missilium contra aeronaves circa basim tuam dele."

msgid "Fly to the LZ, then head overland to destroy the SAM sites."
msgstr "Ad zonam appulsus vola, deinde per terram progredere ut stationes missilium deleas."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Establish Safe Haven"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Constitue Refugium Tutum"

msgid "We can confirm a missile is heading for Alpha Base."
msgstr "Confirmare possumus missile Basim Alpha petere."

msgid "You are to establish a safe haven for evacuation of Beta Base."
msgstr "Refugium tutum ad evacuationem Basis Beta constituere debes."

msgid "Eradicate any enemy and secure the area."
msgstr "Hostes quoslibet dele et regionem tuere."

msgid "Once a safe haven is established, return to the LZ for further orders."
msgstr "Cum refugium tutum constitutum erit, ad zonam appulsus redi ut plura mandata accipias."

msgid "BETA BASE MISSION: Survive and evacuate! Bring a truck"
msgstr "MISSIO BASIS BETA: Supervive et evacua! Affer autocarrum"

msgid "Commander, we have grave news."
msgstr "Praefecte, gravia nova habemus."

msgid "Alpha base has been destroyed by nuclear missile attack."
msgstr "Basis Alpha impetu missilis nuclearis deleta est."

msgid "The Collective are unaware of the nuclear attack and have air units heading for your base."
msgstr "Communitas impetum nuclearem ignorat, et copiae aeriae eius ad basim tuam contendunt."

msgid "This message was intercepted a few moments ago..."
msgstr "Hic nuntius paucis momentis ante interceptus est..."

msgid "You must transport as many of your forces as possible."
msgstr "Quam plurimas copias tuas transvehere debes."

msgid "Good luck, Commander."
msgstr "Bonam fortunam, Praefecte."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Northern Sector"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Sector Septentrionalis"

msgid "Congratulations on your successful evacuation of Beta Base."
msgstr "Gratulamur tibi de felici evacuatione Basis Beta."

msgid "NEXUS has gained access to nuclear weapons and is determined to destroy the Project."
msgstr "NEXUS ad arma nuclearia accessum nactus est et Inceptum delere constituit."

msgid "Take your forces to the Northern Sector"
msgstr "Duc copias tuas ad Sectorem Septentrionalem"

msgid "Once at the mountains secure an LZ. Then establish a forward base."
msgstr "Cum ad montes perveneris, zonam appulsus firma. Deinde basim anteriorem constitue."

msgid "Team Gamma will contact you there."
msgstr "Turma Gamma te ibi conveniet."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Establish A Forward Base"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Constitue Basim Anteriorem"

msgid "Commander, the success of the Project lies with you."
msgstr "Praefecte, successus Incepti in te situs est."

msgid "Secure an LZ, then establish a forward base."
msgstr "Zonam appulsus firma, deinde basim anteriorem constitue."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Missile Launch Site Coordinates"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Coordinatae Loci Emissionis Missilium"

msgid "We have located the site of the missile launches."
msgstr "Locum emissionis missilium invenimus."

msgid "There were one or more missiles at this NASDA site."
msgstr "Unum vel plura missilia in hoc loco NASDA erant."

msgid "We are transmitting coordinates of an LZ near the silos."
msgstr "Coordinatas zonae appulsus prope silos transmittimus."

msgid "Coordinate Download Completed."
msgstr "Oneratio Coordinatarum Completa."

msgid "Secure your LZ, then head overland to destroy the missile silo."
msgstr "Zonam appulsus tuam firma, deinde per terram progredere ut sirum missilium deleas."

msgid "NORTHERN SECTOR MISSION: Nuclear Blast"
msgstr "MISSIO SECTORIS SEPTENTRIONALIS: Displosio Nuclearis"

msgid "All units must escape the area before the warhead detonates."
msgstr "Omnes copiae ex regione effugere debent antequam caput bellicum displodat."

msgid "Air-lift by transport is not possible. You'll have to head overland."
msgstr "Evectio aeria per transvectorium fieri non potest. Per terram progredi debebis."

msgid "The mountain range to the east should shield you from the blast."
msgstr "Iuga montium ad orientem te a displosione protegere debent."

msgid "The valley is your only chance of escape."
msgstr "Vallis sola tua effugiendi occasio est."

msgid "AWAY TEAM UPDATE"
msgstr "NOVA TURMAE ABSENTIS"

msgid "All communication with the away team was lost after the nuclear explosions."
msgstr "Omnis communicatio cum turma absente post displosiones nucleares amissa est."

msgid "Their last transmission indicated they were heading back to base."
msgstr "Ultima eorum transmissio indicavit eos ad basim redire."

msgid "NORTHERN SECTOR MISSION: Assist Team Gamma"
msgstr "MISSIO SECTORIS SEPTENTRIONALIS: Adiuva Turmam Gamma"

msgid "You are to assist Team Gamma."
msgstr "Turmae Gamma auxilium ferre debes."

msgid "On reaching Gamma Base, help secure the area from further NEXUS attacks."
msgstr "Cum ad Basim Gamma perveneris, adiuva ut regio ab ulterioribus impetibus NEXUS muniatur."

msgid "NEXUS DEFEATED"
msgstr "NEXUS VICTUS"

msgid "Commander, we have defeated NEXUS."
msgstr "Praefecte, NEXUS vicimus."

msgid "Unfortunately, our systems' performance has been affected by NEXUS. We are trying to rectify this."
msgstr "Pro dolor, operatio systematum nostrorum a NEXUS impedita est. Hoc corrigere conamur."

msgid "We are currently receiving this transmission."
msgstr "Hanc transmissionem nunc accipimus."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Team Alpha Detected"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Turma Alpha Deprehensa"

msgid "Take a scout force to these coordinates and evaluate the situation."
msgstr "Duc manum exploratoriam ad has coordinatas et statum aestima."

msgid "Determine whether they are Team Alpha. If so, rescue and escort them back to the LZ."
msgstr "Cognosce num Turma Alpha sint. Si ita est, eos serva et ad zonam appulsus reduc."

msgid "This group are part of Team Alpha, Rescue them and escort them to the LZ."
msgstr "Hic grex pars Turmae Alpha est. Eos serva et ad zonam appulsus deduc."

msgid "NORTHERN SECTOR MISSION: Team Alpha Debrief"
msgstr "MISSIO SECTORIS SEPTENTRIONALIS: Relatio Turmae Alpha"

msgid "Team Alpha power transfer in progress."
msgstr "Translatio potentiae Turmae Alpha procedit."

msgid "Commander, after you left the Western Sector we recovered this artifact."
msgstr "Praefecte, postquam Sectorem Occidentalem reliquisti, hoc artificium recuperavimus."

msgid "The benefits from researching it could be vast."
msgstr "Beneficia ex eo investigando ingentia esse possent."

msgid "Enemy forces are ....... from these coordinates."
msgstr "Copiae hostium ....... ab his coordinatis."

msgid "Defend the base and ........ the ......."
msgstr "Defende basim et ........ ......."

msgid "Search and destroy ...."
msgstr "Quaere et dele ...."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Ambush NEXUS Forces"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Insidiare Copiis NEXUS"

msgid "Commander, your decisive actions halted the spread of NEXUS."
msgstr "Praefecte, actiones tuae decretoriae propagationem NEXUS represserunt."

msgid "Before NEXUS was expelled, we intercepted this message - Decoding completed."
msgstr "Antequam NEXUS expulsus est, hunc nuntium intercepimus - Deciphratio completa."

msgid "A NEXUS task force is heading for these coordinates."
msgstr "Manus NEXUS ad has coordinatas contendit."

msgid "You have an opportunity to destroy NEXUS before they get there."
msgstr "Occasionem habes NEXUS delendi antequam eo perveniant."

msgid "Take an attack force and ambush NEXUS task force at ....... the  ......."
msgstr "Cape manum oppugnatoriam et insidiare manui NEXUS apud ....... ......."

msgid "TRANSPORT MISSION: Away Team"
msgstr "MISSIO TRANSVECTORII: Turma Absens"

msgid "Commander, your attack on ...."
msgstr "Praefecte, impetus tuus in ...."

msgid "NEXUS exiting system."
msgstr "NEXUS e systemate exit."

msgid "Incoming transmission from away team."
msgstr "Transmissio adveniens a turma absente."

msgid "Commander, we are attempting to return to base."
msgstr "Praefecte, ad basim redire conamur."

msgid "This is our current position."
msgstr "Haec est positio nostra praesens."

msgid "Take control of our forces and lead us."
msgstr "Cape imperium copiarum nostrarum et nos duc."

msgid "Control transfer successful."
msgstr "Translatio imperii felix."

msgid "Entering new zone."
