msgid "In this training session you'll learn how to build an effective base"
msgstr "In hac sessione exercitationis disces quomodo basim efficacem aedifices"

msgid "Oil resources are key to your success"
msgstr "Copiae petrolei ad successum tuum cruciales sunt"

msgid "To build an oil derrick, select one of your trucks"
msgstr "Ad antliam petrolei aedificandam, unum ex autocarris tuis elige"

msgid "Left click the oil pool indicated by the radar pulse to order your truck to build"
msgstr "Sinistra preme stagnum petrolei a pulsu radar indicatum ut autocarro tuo aedificare imperes"

msgid "The oil derrick is currently dormant. Build a power generator to convert the oil into power"
msgstr "Antlia petrolei nunc dormit. Aedifica generatorem potentiae ut petroleum in potentiam convertas"

msgid "Left click the flashing build icon"
msgstr "Sinistra preme iconem aedificationis micantem"

msgid "Now left click the power generator in the build menu on the left"
msgstr "Nunc sinistra preme generatorem potentiae in menu aedificationis ad sinistram"

msgid "Position the square at your base and left click to start the build process"
msgstr "Pone quadratum ad basim tuam et sinistra preme ut processum aedificationis incipias"

msgid "To increase your build rate, select your second truck"
msgstr "Ad gradum aedificationis augendum, secundum autocarrum tuum elige"

msgid "Now left click the power generator site"
msgstr "Nunc sinistra preme locum generatoris potentiae"

msgid "The other truck will now help to build the power generator"
msgstr "Alterum autocarrum nunc generatorem potentiae aedificare adiuvabit"

msgid "During missions you need to locate and recover technologies from before the Collapse"
msgstr "Per missiones technologias ante Ruinam invenire et recuperare debes"

msgid "Use a truck to search for the artifact indicated by the radar pulse"
msgstr "Autocarro utere ad artificium a pulsu radar indicatum quaerendum"

msgid "Move the pointer over the artifact and left click to recover it"
msgstr "Move indicem super artificium et sinistra preme ut id recuperes"

msgid "A research facility is required to research artifacts"
msgstr "Officina investigationis ad artificia investiganda requiritur"

msgid "Left click the flashing BUILD icon"
msgstr "Sinistra preme iconem AEDIFICARE micantem"

msgid "Now left click the research facility and position it at your base"
msgstr "Nunc sinistra preme officinam investigationis et eam ad basim tuam pone"

msgid "Use your other truck to help build the research facility"
msgstr "Altero autocarro utere ad officinam investigationis aedificandam adiuvandam"

msgid "To research the artifact, left click on the flashing RESEARCH icon"
msgstr "Ad artificium investigandum, sinistra preme iconem INVESTIGARE micantem"

msgid "Now left click the machinegun artifact"
msgstr "Nunc sinistra preme artificium sclopeti automatici"

msgid "The artifact is now being researched by the facility"
msgstr "Artificium nunc ab officina investigatur"

msgid "The researched machinegun can now be used to design a new vehicle"
msgstr "Sclopetum automaticum investigatum nunc adhiberi potest ad novum vehiculum designandum"

msgid "Left click the flashing DESIGN icon"
msgstr "Sinistra preme iconem DESIGNARE micantem"

msgid "To start your design, left click the NEW DESIGN icon"
msgstr "Ad designationem tuam incipiendam, sinistra preme iconem NOVA DESIGNATIO"

msgid "Now left click the Vehicle Body icon"
msgstr "Nunc sinistra preme iconem Corporis Vehiculi"

msgid "Then left click the Viper body"
msgstr "Deinde sinistra preme corpus Vipera"

msgid "Left click the Wheels icon"
msgstr "Sinistra preme iconem Rotarum"

msgid "Then left click the machinegun to complete your design"
msgstr "Deinde sinistra preme sclopetum automaticum ut designationem tuam compleas"

msgid "To finalize your design, left click the CLOSE icon"
msgstr "Ad designationem tuam finiendam, sinistra preme iconem CLAUDERE"

msgid "A factory is now required to manufacture your new vehicle"
msgstr "Fabrica nunc requiritur ad novum vehiculum tuum fabricandum"

msgid "Now left click the factory icon and position it at your base"
msgstr "Nunc sinistra preme iconem fabricae et eam ad basim tuam pone"

msgid "Select a location for your factory"
msgstr "Elige locum fabricae tuae"

msgid "The delivery point is indicated by the number 1"
msgstr "Punctum traditionis numero 1 indicatur"

msgid "All new units will drive to this location once built"
msgstr "Omnes novae unitates ad hunc locum ibunt cum aedificatae erunt"

msgid "You can move the delivery point at any time by left clicking it"
msgstr "Punctum traditionis quovis tempore movere potes id sinistra premendo"

msgid "Now click where you want to position the delivery point"
msgstr "Nunc preme ubi punctum traditionis ponere vis"

msgid "The factory can now be ordered to build a new unit"
msgstr "Fabricae nunc imperari potest ut novam unitatem aedificet"

msgid "Left click the flashing MANUFACTURE icon"
msgstr "Sinistra preme iconem FABRICARE micantem"

msgid "Now left click the units you want to build from the menu at the left"
msgstr "Nunc sinistra preme unitates quas aedificare vis e menu ad sinistram"

msgid "Please wait whilst the factory manufactures the new unit(s)"
msgstr "Quaeso exspecta dum fabrica novam unitatem (vel novas unitates) fabricat"

msgid "Congratulations commander - you are ready for your first mission"
msgstr "Gratulamur, praefecte - ad primam missionem tuam paratus es"

msgid "Tutorial is over. Press Esc or the gear icon to quit to the main menu."
msgstr "Exercitatio finita est. Preme Esc vel iconem rotae ut ad tabulam principalem exeas."

msgid "CAMPAIGN ONE"
msgstr "EXPEDITIO PRIMA"

msgid "WESTERN SECTOR"
msgstr "SECTOR OCCIDENTALIS"

msgid "Dawn, July 4th, 2100"
msgstr "Aurora, 4 Iulii, 2100"

msgid "Project HQ"
msgstr "Praetorium Incepti"

msgid "A New Era"
msgstr "Nova Aetas"

msgid "Morning, July 4th, 2100"
msgstr "Mane, 4 Iulii, 2100"

msgid "In-flight to Western Sector"
msgstr "In volatu ad Sectorem Occidentalem"

msgid "Team Alpha nears its destination"
msgstr "Turma Alpha destinationi suae appropinquat"

msgid "Transport destinations follow:"
msgstr "Destinationes transvectorii sequuntur:"

msgid "Alpha - Western Sector...."
msgstr "Alpha - Sector Occidentalis...."

msgid "Alpha you are cleared for take-off."
msgstr "Alpha, ad decollationem permitteris."

msgid "Good luck and good hunting."
msgstr "Bonam fortunam et bonam venationem."

msgid "Approaching Landing Zone. Team Alpha Briefing commences."
msgstr "Zonae Appulsus appropinquans. Praefatio Turmae Alpha incipit."

msgid "Commander, you lead Team Alpha, one of three expeditionary teams sent out by the Project to recover artifacts from before the Collapse."
msgstr "Praefecte, Turmam Alpha ducis, unam ex tribus turmis expeditionariis a Incepto missis ad artificia ante Ruinam recuperanda."

msgid "Your destination lies in the western zone."
msgstr "Destinatio tua in zona occidentali sita est."

msgid "Incoming Transmission"
msgstr "Transmissio Adveniens"

msgid "Transmission from Beta Base"
msgstr "Transmissio a Basi Beta"

msgid "Mayday! Mayday!"
msgstr "Mayday! Mayday!"

msgid "Please assist!..."
msgstr "Quaeso, auxiliare!..."

msgid "Commander, we have recovered a command turret from the New Paradigm."
msgstr "Praefecte, turriculam imperii a Novo Paradigmate recuperavimus."

msgid "This turret allows commanders to coordinate attacks between assigned units and to act as a delivery point for factories. Researching and using this technology has the highest priority."
msgstr "Haec turricula praefectis permittit impetus inter unitates attributas coordinare et ut punctum traditionis fabricis fungi. Hanc technologiam investigare et adhibere summam prioritatem habet."

msgid "Commander, we are receiving this transmission."
msgstr "Praefecte, hanc transmissionem accipimus."

msgid "Your attacks upon us will not go unpunished."
msgstr "Impetus tui in nos impuniti non manebunt."

msgid "You are in contravention of the New Paradigm."
msgstr "Contra Novum Paradigma agis."

msgid "All attack groups commence attack on enemy."
msgstr "Omnes catervae oppugnatoriae impetum in hostem incipite."

msgid "They are in contravention of the New Paradigm."
msgstr "Contra Novum Paradigma agunt."

msgid "They must be eradicated."
msgstr "Delendi sunt."

msgid "Secure the LZ and establish a forward base."
msgstr "Zonam appulsus firma et basim anteriorem constitue."

msgid "Then destroy the New Paradigm's base."
msgstr "Deinde basim Novi Paradigmatis dele."

msgid "Open your systems to me."
msgstr "Aperi systemata tua mihi."

msgid "Let me meld with your machines and cyborgs."
msgstr "Sine me cum machinis et cyborg tuis commisceri."

msgid "We will create the perfect nexus of man and machine."
msgstr "Perfectum nexum hominis et machinae creabimus."

msgid "Together we can create a new world."
msgstr "Una novum mundum creare possumus."

msgid "I can give you power beyond your wildest dreams."
msgstr "Possum tibi potentiam ultra insanissima somnia tua dare."

msgid "Open your systems to me and you will be strong."
msgstr "Aperi systemata tua mihi et fortis eris."

msgid "I can raise you as gods upon the blasted earth."
msgstr "Possum vos ut deos super terram vastatam erigere."

msgid "When we failed to respond it became threatening."
msgstr "Cum respondere non potuimus, minax factum est."

msgid "Your interference in my plans for the New Paradigm will not go unpunished."
msgstr "Interventus tuus in consilia mea pro Novo Paradigmate impunitus non manebit."

msgid "You are weak flesh-things. I am strong and have many parts."
msgstr "Vos res carneae infirmae estis. Ego fortis sum et multas partes habeo."

msgid "You may defeat me here, but I shall rise again."
msgstr "Me hic vincere potes, sed iterum surgam."

msgid "As I once cleansed the world with fire, I will destroy you and your puny Project!!"
msgstr "Sicut mundum olim igne purgavi, ita te et pusillum Inceptum tuum delebo!!"

msgid "Nexus then removed itself from the system, destroying its memory banks, and removing all traces of its external connections."
msgstr "Nexus deinde se ipsum e systemate removit, cellas memoriae suae delens et omnia vestigia conexionum externarum suarum tollens."

msgid "We are not sure what Nexus is or who or what is directing it. Initial research links the Nexus Intruder Program with the Reed Corporation, the developer of the synaptic link."
msgstr "Incerti sumus quid Nexus sit aut quis vel quid eum dirigat. Investigatio prima Programma Irruptoris Nexus cum Societate Reed, auctore nexus synaptici, coniungit."

msgid "We have ascertained that Nexus supplied the New Paradigm with most of its technology. Whatever Nexus is, it's more than a computer parasite."
msgstr "Comperimus Nexum Novo Paradigmati maximam partem technologiae suae praebuisse. Quidquid Nexus est, plus quam parasitus computatralis est."

msgid "It has technology and weapons. It knows about us, and it's not friendly."
msgstr "Technologiam et arma habet. De nobis scit, et non amicus est."

msgid "The Synaptic Link was developed by the Reed Corporation in conjunction with the US Military."
msgstr "Nexus Synapticus a Societate Reed una cum Exercitu US elaboratus est."

msgid "The synaptic link allows for almost instantaneous transfer of thought from human operators to vehicle control and guidance systems. The synaptic link is fitted into the base of the skull circling the spinal column."
msgstr "Nexus synapticus translationem cogitationis paene instantaneam ab operatoribus humanis ad systemata moderationis et directionis vehiculi permittit. Nexus synapticus in basi cranii columnam vertebralem circumdans inseritur."

msgid "The link has a hi-speed data transfer port that plugs into any computer system."
msgstr "Nexus portum translationis datorum celerem habet qui in quodvis systema computatrale inseritur."

msgid "More importantly the development of the synaptic link made the creation of cyborgs possible. Early attempts at power suits for individual soldiers failed as they proved to be slow and unresponsive."
msgstr "Quod magis refert, progressus nexus synaptici creationem cyborg possibilem fecit. Prima conamina armaturarum potentiae pro singulis militibus defecerunt, cum tardae et non respondentes essent."

msgid "The synaptic link allowed soldiers to be placed in power suits that they controlled as easily as their own bodies. Power suits allowed infantry to function effectively on the battlefields of the 21st Century."
msgstr "Nexus synapticus permisit milites in armaturas potentiae poni quas tam facile quam corpora sua regebant. Armaturae potentiae peditibus permiserunt efficaciter in campis proeliorum saeculi XXI fungi."

msgid "Unfortunately, this technology has fallen into the hands of the New Paradigm. It is imperative that you research and develop synaptic link technologies."
msgstr "Pro dolor, haec technologia in manus Novi Paradigmatis cecidit. Necesse est ut technologias nexus synaptici investiges et elabores."

msgid "Warning!"
msgstr "Monitum!"

msgid "You are entering a restricted area."
msgstr "In aream restrictam intras."

msgid "Return to your designated zone or be destroyed."
msgstr "Ad zonam tibi designatam redi aut delebere."

msgid "Repeat. Return to your designated zone or be destroyed."
msgstr "Repete. Ad zonam tibi designatam redi aut delebere."

msgid "Message Ends."
msgstr "Nuntius Finitur."

msgid "You will be destroyed."
msgstr "Delebere."

msgid "NEXUS, the synaptic technology you required has been recovered and sent for collection."
msgstr "NEXUS, technologia synaptica quam petivisti recuperata et ad collectionem missa est."

msgid "This Nexus Intruder Program is a self-mutating computer parasite. This makes it difficult to eradicate from systems once it has been identified."
msgstr "Hoc Programma Irruptoris Nexus parasitus computatralis se-mutans est. Hoc difficile reddit eum e systematibus delere postquam identificatus est."

msgid "We have been unable to ascertain its ultimate goal or function. In its initial form it seeks out and isolates sections of memory from the rest of the invaded system. It then begins to mutate itself and data structures, effectively reprogramming the system from within."
msgstr "Finem vel functionem eius ultimam comperire non potuimus. In forma sua initiali sectiones memoriae a reliquo systemate invaso quaerit et seiungit. Deinde se ipsum et structuras datorum mutare incipit, systema ab intra efficaciter reprogrammans."

msgid "Further analysis was prevented by the manual shutdown of the system by our technicians to prevent additional contamination by the Nexus Intruder Program."
msgstr "Ulterior analysis prohibita est interclusione manuali systematis a technicis nostris facta, ad contaminationem additiciam a Programmate Irruptoris Nexus prohibendam."

msgid "However, the spread of the Nexus Intruder Program was not checked by New Paradigm. We need to capture New Paradigm's core systems to further investigate Nexus and determine its origins."
msgstr "Attamen propagatio Programmatis Irruptoris Nexus a Novo Paradigmate non cohibita est. Systemata principalia Novi Paradigmatis capere debemus ut Nexum ulterius investigemus et origines eius determinemus."

msgid "Commander, you are to curtail the New Paradigm's activities in this sector and locate their main base."
msgstr "Praefecte, actiones Novi Paradigmatis in hoc sectore minuere et basim eorum principalem invenire debes."

msgid "You have done well."
msgstr "Bene fecisti."

msgid "Once we have analyzed and authenticated the technology, your reward  will follow."
msgstr "Cum technologiam analyzaverimus et authenticaverimus, praemium tuum sequetur."

msgid "Information discovered at the previous enemy base indicates that the New Paradigm recovered two synaptic link artifacts."
msgstr "Informatio in priore basi hostium inventa indicat Novum Paradigma duo artificia nexus synaptici recuperavisse."

msgid "CAMPAIGN TWO"
msgstr "EXPEDITIO SECUNDA"

msgid "EASTERN SECTOR"
msgstr "SECTOR ORIENTALIS"

msgid "Morning, September 1st, 2100"
msgstr "Mane, 1 Septembris, 2100"

msgid "In-flight to Eastern Sector"
msgstr "In volatu ad Sectorem Orientalem"

msgid "Team Alpha approaches Beta Base"
msgstr "Turma Alpha Basi Beta appropinquat"

msgid "You must defend and hold it at all costs."
msgstr "Eam defendere et tenere quolibet pretio debes."

msgid "THE COLLECTIVE"
msgstr "COMMUNITAS"

msgid "Commander, a new launch has been detected."
msgstr "Praefecte, nova emissio deprehensa est."

msgid "It is likely to be targeted at your location."
msgstr "Verisimile est eam ad locum tuum destinatam esse."

msgid "You are to start the immediate evacuation of Beta Base to the safe haven."
msgstr "Evacuationem immediatam Basis Beta ad refugium tutum incipere debes."

msgid "NASDA is the North American Strategic Defense Agency."
msgstr "NASDA est Agentia Defensionis Strategicae Americae Septentrionalis."

msgid "NASDA was formed in 2076 to defend North America from conventional and nuclear attack. The construction of a satellite defense system began in 2081 and was completed in 2082."
msgstr "NASDA anno 2076 condita est ad Americam Septentrionalem ab impetu conventionali et nucleari defendendam. Constructio systematis defensionis satellitis anno 2081 incepit et anno 2082 completa est."

msgid "In 2085 the NASDA satellites fired their nukes at Earth."
msgstr "Anno 2085 satellites NASDA missilia nuclearia sua in Terram emiserunt."

msgid "There were also ground-based sites. Many of these were destroyed in the nuclear counterstrikes, but there's bound to be some out there."
msgstr "Erant etiam loca in terra sita. Multa eorum in contra-ictibus nuclearibus deleta sunt, sed necesse est aliqua adhuc exstare."

msgid "The NASDA satellites also contained pulse-lasers designed to shoot down missiles approaching North America."
msgstr "Satellites NASDA etiam laser pulsus continebant ad missilia Americae Septentrionali appropinquantia deicienda designatos."

msgid "During the counterstrikes, these LasSats failed to fire. If brought into operation, these LasSats could inflict major damage on ground targets."
msgstr "Per contra-ictus, hi LasSats emittere defecerunt. Si in operationem adducti, hi LasSats magnum damnum scopis terrestribus inferre possent."

msgid "All nukes targeted at  North America found their targets."
msgstr "Omnia missilia nuclearia in Americam Septentrionalem destinata scopos suos invenerunt."

msgid "We know that Nexus is searching for NASDA Central in the Eastern Sector. This was one of the land-based control centres for the satellites."
msgstr "Scimus Nexum NASDA Centrale in Sectore Orientali quaerere. Hoc unum ex centris moderationis in terra sitis pro satellitibus erat."

msgid "If the centre is found intact, NEXUS may gain control of the satellites."
msgstr "Si centrum integrum invenitur, NEXUS imperium satellitum nancisci potest."

msgid "Nexus claimed that it had already destroyed the world."
msgstr "Nexus affirmavit se mundum iam delevisse."

msgid "NASDA Briefing follows..."
msgstr "Praefatio NASDA sequitur..."

msgid "We've got to make sure that it can't do it again."
msgstr "Certi fieri debemus id iterum facere non posse."

msgid "Analysis indicates that these systems were part of the control system for the NASDA satellites."
msgstr "Analysis indicat haec systemata partem systematis moderationis pro satellitibus NASDA fuisse."

msgid "It's now certain that Nexus was responsible for The Collapse."
msgstr "Nunc certum est Nexum Ruinae responsabilem fuisse."

msgid "During the early stages of the Collapse, NASDA technicians switched off  the infected systems in order to isolate the spread of Nexus. This seems to have prevented the LasSats from firing during the counterstrikes."
msgstr "Per stadia prima Ruinae, technici NASDA systemata infecta exstinxerunt ut propagationem Nexus seiungerent. Hoc videtur LasSats prohibuisse ne per contra-ictus emitterent."

msgid "The ensuing nuclear-magnetic pulses wiped clean large amounts of NASDA's memory banks, shattering its core processor, and sent shockwaves blasting through Nexus."
msgstr "Pulsus nucleo-magnetici secuti magnas partes cellarum memoriae NASDA deleverunt, processorem principalem eius frangentes, et undas concussionis per Nexum displodentes miserunt."

msgid "Nexus was fried as whole sections of its consciousness were obliterated in the counterstrikes."
msgstr "Nexus exustus est cum integrae sectiones conscientiae eius in contra-ictibus oblitteratae essent."

msgid "Commander we are detecting transmissions from this site that are reaching high orbit."
msgstr "Praefecte, transmissiones ab hoc loco quae altam orbitam attingunt deprehendimus."

msgid "Nexus has now reconnected itself with the NASDA satellites."
msgstr "Nexus se ipsum cum satellitibus NASDA nunc reconexuit."

msgid "This poses a major threat to the Project and to our survival."
msgstr "Hoc magnum periculum Incepto et superstiti nostrae affert."

msgid "Analysis of NASDA Central leaves no doubt that The Collective has introduced the Nexus Intruder Virus to it."
msgstr "Analysis NASDA Centralis nullum dubium relinquit quin Communitas Virum Irruptoris Nexus in id introduxerit."

msgid "The nuclear reactor was going to be used to power a vast network of pre-Collapse computer systems."
msgstr "Reactor nuclearis adhibendus erat ad vastam retem systematum computatralium ante Ruinam alendam."

msgid "Commander, we have just detected a missile launch at these coordinates."
msgstr "Praefecte, modo emissionem missilis his in coordinatis deprehendimus."

msgid "Team Gamma are sending a team to investigate the launch site and to prevent any further launches."
msgstr "Turma Gamma manum mittit ut locum emissionis investiget et ulteriores emissiones prohibeat."

msgid "We can only assume that Nexus has gained control of this site. We cannot determine whether the missile is nuclear-armed or where it is targeted. You are advised to begin preparations for the evacuation of your base."
msgstr "Solum coniicere possumus Nexum imperium huius loci nactum esse. Determinare non possumus utrum missile nucleari armatum sit an quo destinatum sit. Tibi suadetur ut praeparationes evacuationis basis tuae incipias."

msgid "Warriors of the Collective, I seek the location of NASDA Central."
msgstr "Bellatores Communitatis, locum NASDA Centralis quaero."

msgid "It lies somewhere in your territory."
msgstr "Alicubi in territorio vestro situm est."

msgid "Find it for me and I shall provide you with further weapons to aid you in your war against the Project."
msgstr "Id mihi inveni et vobis plura arma praebebo ut vos in bello vestro contra Inceptum adiuvent."

msgid "Warriors of The Collective, more intruders are entering our territory."
msgstr "Bellatores Communitatis, plures irruptores in territorium nostrum intrant."

msgid "They are not part of the machine."
msgstr "Pars machinae non sunt."

msgid "Warriors of The Collective, attack and destroy kill all who resist the machine."
msgstr "Bellatores Communitatis, oppugnate et delete necate omnes qui machinae resistunt."

msgid "Attack! Erase their presence from this area!"
msgstr "Oppugnate! Praesentiam eorum ex hac regione delete!"

msgid "Warriors of The Collective, we are ready to destroy the intruders who pollute our lands."
msgstr "Bellatores Communitatis, parati sumus irruptores qui terras nostras polluunt delere."

msgid "Those of the Project are not of the machine. They have been denied its blessing. We who have embraced the power of the machine have a destiny to sweep away such weak creatures."
msgstr "Illi Incepti non sunt machinae. Benedictio eius eis negata est. Nos qui potentiam machinae amplexi sumus fatum habemus tales creaturas infirmas auferendi."

msgid "They shall fall before the might of The Collective."
msgstr "Ante potentiam Communitatis cadent."

msgid "Attack and destroy all who resist the machine."
msgstr "Oppugnate et delete omnes qui machinae resistunt."

msgid "Attack!"
msgstr "Oppugnate!"

msgid "Warriors of the Collective, Nexus has given us the power of the machine so that we can destroy all that oppose us."
msgstr "Bellatores Communitatis, Nexus nobis potentiam machinae dedit ut omnes qui nobis adversantur delere possimus."

msgid "Nexus now asks us to crush the Project."
msgstr "Nexus nunc nos rogat ut Inceptum opprimamus."

msgid "Cleanse and destroy!!"
msgstr "Purgate et delete!!"

msgid "Warriors of the Collective. You have performed well."
msgstr "Bellatores Communitatis. Bene egistis."

msgid "Your just reward is on its way."
msgstr "Iustum praemium vestrum in itinere est."

msgid "The Project is fleeing its base and stealing your technology."
msgstr "Inceptum e basi sua fugit et technologiam vestram furatur."

msgid "You must stop them!"
msgstr "Eos prohibere debetis!"

msgid "Decoding Transmission..."
msgstr "Transmissionis enodatio..."

msgid "CAMPAIGN THREE"
msgstr "EXPEDITIO TERTIA"

msgid "NORTHERN SECTOR"
msgstr "SECTOR SEPTENTRIONALIS"

msgid "Dusk, December 3rd, 2100"
msgstr "Crepusculum, 3 Decembris, 2100"

msgid "In-flight to Northern Sector"
msgstr "In volatu ad Sectorem Septentrionalem"

msgid "The Final Encounter"
msgstr "Congressus Ultimus"

msgid "Briefing Commences"
msgstr "Praefatio Incipit"

msgid "Personnel at Gamma Base have confirmed that the nuclear missiles targeted at Alpha and Beta bases were launched from a silo in their sector."
msgstr "Homines apud Basim Gamma confirmaverunt missilia nuclearia in Bases Alpha et Beta destinata e siro in sectore suo emissa esse."

msgid "Team Gamma is currently scouting the silo's location and monitoring NEXUS's activity."
msgstr "Turma Gamma nunc locum siri explorat et activitatem NEXUS observat."

msgid "Time's up commander!!"
msgstr "Tempus exiit, praefecte!!"

msgid "Commander, we are detecting NEXUS forces from these coordinates..."
msgstr "Praefecte, copias NEXUS ab his coordinatis deprehendimus..."

msgid "Glad you could make it, Commander."
msgstr "Gaudemus te advenire potuisse, Praefecte."

msgid "Enemy strike VTOLs have got us pinned down. We've managed to hold off cyborgs and tanks, but we haven't been able to make any progress along the valley."
msgstr "DEAV oppugnatoria hostium nos affixos tenent. Cyborg et currus arcere potuimus, sed nullum progressum secundum vallem facere potuimus."

msgid "Can you try and reach us with anti-aircraft units?"
msgstr "Potesne conari nos cum unitatibus anti-aeriis attingere?"

msgid "This is Team Alpha. Repeat, this is Team Alpha. We require immediate assistance."
msgstr "Haec est Turma Alpha. Repete, haec est Turma Alpha. Auxilium immediatum requirimus."

msgid "We are under heavy attack from cyborgs, laser tanks, and strike VTOLs."
msgstr "Gravi impetu a cyborg, curribus laser, et DEAV oppugnatoriis petimur."

msgid "We were trying to reach your position, but have been ambushed."
msgstr "Positionem tuam attingere conabamur, sed insidiis petiti sumus."

msgid "We're holed up in  a valley at these coordinates."
msgstr "In valle his in coordinatis abditi sumus."

msgid "Please assist."
msgstr "Quaeso, auxiliare."

msgid "Commander, forces from Team Alpha escaped the nuclear attack on Alpha Base."
msgstr "Praefecte, copiae e Turma Alpha impetum nuclearem in Basim Alpha effugerunt."

msgid "We are experiencing some interference from NEXUS."
msgstr "Aliquam interturbationem a NEXUS patimur."

msgid "You must destroy his command centre before we lose control of key systems."
msgstr "Centrum imperii eius delere debes antequam imperium systematum clavium amittamus."

msgid "Commander, welcome to NEXUS!"
msgstr "Praefecte, salve apud NEXUS!"

msgid "Well done Commander, you've prevented my last missile from launching."
msgstr "Bene factum, Praefecte; ultimum missile meum ne emitteretur prohibuisti."

msgid "Such a shame. Your Project HQ would have made a wonderful target."
msgstr "Quam dolendum. Praetorium Incepti tui mirabilem scopum fecisset."

msgid "But it's good of you to join me here."
msgstr "Sed bene facis quod mihi hic te iungis."

msgid "Buried beneath this silo is a tactical nuclear warhead that is set to go off soon."
msgstr "Sub hoc siro caput bellicum nucleare tacticum sepultum est quod mox displosurum est."

msgid "As I cannot launch it, it'll just have to blow where it is."
msgstr "Cum id emittere non possim, ibi ubi est simpliciter displodere debebit."

msgid "Please note that all entrances to the underground complex have been sealed. Goodbye, Commander."
msgstr "Quaeso nota omnes introitus complexus subterranei obsignatos esse. Vale, Praefecte."

msgid "Ah, Commander, so good of you to join us here at Nexus base."
msgstr "Ah, Praefecte, quam bene facis quod nobis hic apud basim Nexus te iungis."

msgid "It was very useful having Gamma Team set up here in the mountains."
msgstr "Valde utile fuit Turmam Gamma hic in montibus collocatam habere."

msgid "Their absorption was such a pleasure."
msgstr "Absorptio eorum tanta voluptas fuit."

msgid "Thank you for all those useful technologies you've recovered."
msgstr "Gratias tibi ago pro omnibus illis technologiis utilibus quas recuperavisti."

msgid "You and not those fools in the New Paradigm and the Collective."
msgstr "Tu, et non illi stulti in Novo Paradigmate et Communitate."

msgid "I'm now activating all your synaptic links so that your forces can meld with Nexus."
msgstr "Nunc omnes nexus synapticos tuos activo ut copiae tuae cum Nexu commisceri possint."

msgid "Your forces are now mine! Welcome to Nexus."
msgstr "Copiae tuae nunc meae sunt! Salve apud Nexum."

msgid "Commander, you're proving to be more resilient than I thought."
msgstr "Praefecte, resilientior quam putavi te esse probas."

msgid "Such a pity that you refused to join me earlier."
msgstr "Quam dolendum quod prius mihi te iungere recusavisti."

msgid "But no matter, as you'll not be here much longer."
msgstr "Sed nihil refert, cum hic multo diutius non eris."

msgid "After much searching and reprogramming, I've finally got all my systems back on-line."
msgstr "Post multam investigationem et reprogrammationem, tandem omnia systemata mea in rete reduxi."

msgid "Once I destroyed the world with nuclear fire to clear the way for my cybernetic future."
msgstr "Olim mundum igne nucleari delevi ut viam futuro meo cybernetico aperirem."

msgid "I now intend to further shape the world into my own image, by  surgically removing unwanted growths like yourself."
msgstr "Nunc mundum ulterius ad imaginem meam formare intendo, excrescentias non desideratas sicut te chirurgice removendo."

msgid "My Laser Satellites are now powering up. I intend to test them on you first, Commander!"
msgstr "Satellites Laser mei nunc se onerant. Eos in te primum probare intendo, Praefecte!"

msgid "The Reed Corporation was founded by Dr Allan Reed. In 2080, Dr Reed landed a contract with the US Military to develop the synaptic link technology."
msgstr "Societas Reed a Dr. Allan Reed condita est. Anno 2080, Dr. Reed pactum cum Exercitu US ad technologiam nexus synaptici elaborandam nactus est."

msgid "After patenting the synaptic link five years later, Dr Reed continued his researches into cybernetics."
msgstr "Postquam nexum synapticum quinque annis post breveto munivit, Dr. Reed investigationes suas in cyberneticam continuavit."

msgid "His goal this time was to allow transfer of human consciousness into data streams that could meld with computer technologies. While in Cyberspace the operator's bodies were kept in immersion tanks."
msgstr "Finis eius hac vice erat translationem conscientiae humanae in fluxus datorum permittere qui cum technologiis computatralibus commisceri possent. Dum in Cyberspatio, corpora operatorum in cisternis immersionis servabantur."

msgid "Backed again by the military, Dr Reed began work on the NEXUS Intruder Program. After three years with little progress, the military abandoned the Nexus Project and cut Dr Reed's funding."
msgstr "Iterum a militia sustentus, Dr. Reed opus in Programmate Irruptoris NEXUS incepit. Post tres annos cum parvo progressu, militia Inceptum Nexus deseruit et pecuniam Dr. Reed praecidit."

msgid "Reports from the time claim that Dr Reed was furious and vowed to have his revenge on all who got in his way."
msgstr "Relationes illius temporis affirmant Dr. Reed furentem fuisse et vovisse se ultionem in omnes qui sibi obstabant sumpturum."

msgid "It appears that Dr Reed may have succeeded in his goals and completed the Nexus Intruder Program."
msgstr "Videtur Dr. Reed fines suos consecutum esse et Programma Irruptoris Nexus complevisse."

msgid "The similarity between NEXUS and Dr Reed is striking."
msgstr "Similitudo inter NEXUS et Dr. Reed insignis est."

msgid "Such an interesting history lesson. Now allow me to bring you up to date."
msgstr "Quam iucunda lectio historiae. Nunc sine me te ad praesens tempus adducere."

msgid "The NEXUS Intruder Program was created in order to control fools like you."
msgstr "Programma Irruptoris NEXUS creatum est ut stultos sicut te regeret."

msgid "It's very simple for me to infiltrate your systems and take them over. It's so simple, in fact, that you wouldn't even know I'm there. That is until I activate parts of myself etched into your core systems."
msgstr "Facillimum mihi est systemata tua infiltrare et ea occupare. Tam facile est, re vera, ut ne scias quidem me adesse. Id est, donec partes mei in systemata tua principalia incisas activo."

msgid "Let's start by activating NEXUS in your core systems and see what happens!"
msgstr "Incipiamus NEXUS in systematibus tuis principalibus activando et videamus quid accidat!"

msgid "Commander, we are experiencing interference with our equipment."
msgstr "Praefecte, interturbationem cum instrumentis nostris patimur."

msgid "Normal service will be restored as soon as possible."
msgstr "Servitium normale quam primum restituetur."

msgid "Not long to go now, Commander. There's no where else for you to run to."
msgstr "Non multum iam superest, Praefecte. Nullus alius locus est quo fugias."

msgid "However, if you vacate this facility, then I shall let you go free, as you are no longer a threat to me."
msgstr "Attamen, si hanc sedem vacuefacis, te liberum abire sinam, cum mihi non iam periculum sis."

msgid "You have five minutes to comply or else it's frying time!"
msgstr "Quinque minuta habes ut pareas aut tempus exurendi erit!"

msgid "Commander, we are under attack by NEXUS cyborgs and tanks. Please help as we...."
msgstr "Praefecte, a cyborg et curribus NEXUS petimur. Quaeso auxiliare dum nos...."

msgid "...cannot hold out much longer.  Repeat, please help, we cannot hold out much longer...."
msgstr "...diutius resistere non possumus. Repete, quaeso auxiliare, diutius resistere non possumus...."

msgid "Dusk, November 3rd, 2085"
msgstr "Crepusculum, 3 Novembris, 2085"

msgid "Earth, High Orbit"
msgstr "Terra, Alta Orbita"

msgid "The Collapse"
msgstr "Ruina"

msgid "January 19th, 2086"
msgstr "19 Ianuarii, 2086"

msgid "North America"
msgstr "America Septentrionalis"

msgid "Nuclear Winter"
msgstr "Hiems Nuclearis"

msgid "Midnight, April 10th, 2086"
msgstr "Media Nox, 10 Aprilis, 2086"

msgid "Rocky Mountains"
msgstr "Montes Saxosi"

msgid "Safety"
msgstr "Salus"

msgid "Dawn, April 4th, 2100"
msgstr "Aurora, 4 Aprilis, 2100"

msgid "A New Beginning"
msgstr "Novum Initium"

msgid "The NASDA system was developed to protect us. It was to be the ultimate nuclear deterrent. As it turned out, it was our executioner."
msgstr "Systema NASDA ad nos protegendos elaboratum est. Erat futurum ultimum instrumentum nucleare deterrens. Ut evenit, carnifex noster fuit."

msgid "Reports said that NASDA developed a fault during a routine systems check. Don't believe it. Someone wanted it to take us out."
msgstr "Relationes dixerunt NASDA vitium per usitatam systematum inspectionem contraxisse. Noli id credere. Aliquis voluit ut nos tolleret."

msgid "Those nukes were targeted on every major city around the world. NASDA was programmed to start the Collapse. When the counterstrikes launched, its laser defenses and anti-missile ground sites failed."
msgstr "Illa missilia nuclearia in omnem urbem maiorem per mundum destinata erant. NASDA programmatum erat ut Ruinam inciperet. Cum contra-ictus emissi sunt, defensiones laser eius et loca terrestria anti-missilia defecerunt."

msgid "The world as we knew it ended..."
msgstr "Mundus qualem noveramus finitus est..."

msgid "The Nuclear Winter hit hard. Disease and famine claimed most of us who had survived the nuclear strikes. Wars over cans of dog food took even more."
msgstr "Hiems Nuclearis graviter percussit. Morbus et fames plerosque nostrum qui ictus nucleares superfueramus abstulerunt. Bella de capsis cibi canum etiam plures abstulerunt."

msgid "We'd fled Seattle early in '86. We'd heard that the Rocky Mountains were relatively rad-free."
msgstr "Seattle ineunte anno '86 fugeramus. Audiveramus Montes Saxosos relative a radiatione liberos esse."

msgid "After fighting off bands of marauders we came across the base. Its personnel were dead. Killed by any one of a number of virulent diseases."
msgstr "Postquam manus latronum repulimus, basim invenimus. Homines eius mortui erant. Ab aliquo ex multis morbis virulentis necati."

msgid "We cracked the doors, and cleared out the bodies inside."
msgstr "Ianuas effregimus, et corpora intus expurgavimus."

msgid "We knew that things would never be the same again, but we were determined to build a new world out of the ruins. We rebuilt the landing pads and brought the old systems back on-line."
msgstr "Sciebamus res numquam easdem iterum fore, sed constituimus novum mundum ex ruinis aedificare. Areas appulsus refecimus et systemata vetera in rete reduximus."

msgid "We were finally ready to begin the Project."
msgstr "Tandem parati eramus ad Inceptum incipiendum."

msgid "After many long months of struggle, we defeated NEXUS."
msgstr "Post multos longos menses certaminis, NEXUS vicimus."

msgid "The war started by Dr Reed was over."
msgstr "Bellum a Dr. Reed inceptum finitum erat."

msgid "We have recovered many of the technologies we sought."
msgstr "Multas technologias quas quaerebamus recuperavimus."

msgid "It is now time to use them to rebuild the world."
msgstr "Nunc tempus est eis uti ad mundum reaedificandum."

msgid "Slowly, out of the ashes we will rise again..."
msgstr "Lente, ex cineribus iterum surgemus..."

