msgid "Timer Power Bonus"
msgstr "Beneficium Potentiae Horologii"

msgid "Grant power based on the remaining level timer, so there's no need to wait out the clock."
msgstr "Dat potentiam ex horologio gradus reliquo, ut horologium exspectare non opus sit."

