msgstr "Auto-Servationes-Tantum"

msgid "Disable the ability to manually save / quick-save, limit autosaves to the beginning of each level."
msgstr "Inactiva facultatem manualiter servandi / celeriter servandi, limita auto-servationes ad initium cuiusque gradus."

