msgid "The classic terrain appearance from the initial release. Low-resolution, pixel-art textures."
msgstr "Species terreni classica ex emissione initiali. Texturae humilis resolutionis, pixel-art."

msgid "The normal terrain appearance used as the default for more than a decade. Higher-resolution, recreated textures."
msgstr "Species terreni normalis ut defalta per plus quam decennium adhibita. Texturae altioris resolutionis, recreatae."

msgid "The remastered, high-quality terrain appearance. High-resolution, with modern bump + specular mapping. Requires more memory and a better GPU."
msgstr "Species terreni refecta, altae qualitatis. Altae resolutionis, cum mappatione moderna bump + specularis. Plus memoriae et meliorem GPU requirit."

