msgstr "Qualitas Umbrationis Terreni"

msgid "The quality of terrain shading (normal maps, specular highlights, etc). Higher settings improve terrain details at the expense of performance and memory usage."
msgstr "Qualitas umbrationis terreni (mappae normales, lumina specularia, etc). Optiones altiores singula terreni emendant sumptu effectus et usus memoriae."

